jcr:content.awardReq1: Be a registered Girl Scout in the Girl Scouts of Western Washington council Be less than 21 years old Be a Gold Award recipient (or working on the final steps of your approved Gold Award project). If girls are selected as Award of Excellence recipients, but have not yet completed all parts of their Gold Award, funds will not be distributed until Gold Award is completed (must be completed by September 30 or scholarship is forfeit)
